        <body>
            <p>
                <hi rend="underline">
                    <add>ייטיב נא כבודו להודיעני מקח והמחזורים מנהג ספרד מתורגמים ענגליש</add>
                </hi>
            </p>
            <p rend="align(center)"><placeName>N.Y.</placeName>
                <date>July 5, 1867</date>.</p>
            <p><addressee>Rev. Dr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>:</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Please be good enough to let me know the price of holi<lb/>day
                prayer books, Sephardic ritual, with English translation in<lb/> gilt Morocco, also
                how you sold them to booksellers and at<lb/> what price to others and in how many
                volumes they are<lb/> found. Another thing — <sic>sometime</sic> ago I wrote to you
                about<lb/> a small prayer book which you intended to publish. I<lb/> cannot
                understand your failure to reply. Now, if you<lb/> please, be good enough to let me
                know your decision about<lb/> this matter.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">The words your servant, ever ready to serve you, who<lb/> prays for
                your welfare.</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">H. Sakolski</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">
                <placeName>53 Division St.</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="Envelope"/>
            <p>
                <addressee>Red. Dr. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
            </p>
